These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-8-1::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, old-henry, ritmeester
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, swimming, cycling
House: farmhouse, townhouse, cottage
There are 3 different favourite colors: emerald, white, lilac
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, thai, nigerian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, august, january
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: poppy, marigold, lily
 1. the person who's birthday is in august is the person who likes white##1
 2. the malaysian is not the person who likes emerald##6
 3. the farmhouse house is the person who growslily##1
 4. the person who likes white is the person who growsmarigold##1
 5. the thai is somewhere to the right of the malaysian##5
 6. the old-henry-smoker is the townhouse house##1
 7. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 8. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the right of the old-henry-smoker##8
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
10. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the left of the person who likes white##5
11. the person who's birthday is in august is not the thai##6
12. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
13. the person who's sport is rowing is in the middle##1
14. the person who growslily is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |      3      |
| Cigar      | ritmeester      | old-henry  | game |
| Sport          | cycling  | rowing      | swimming        |
| House         | cottage     | townhouse     | farmhouse      |
| Color           | emerald | white | lilac   |
| Nationality   | nigerian      | malaysian | thai   |
| Birthday           | january  | august      | march      |
| Flower     | poppy    | marigold   | lily        |

